race.comment: ATTESTOR (2) finds his race today fifth-up from the inside gate. Stalked the speed with the 59kg when a gritty third over 1600m at Nowra. Buckley sticks and should prove too good for these. ALL TOO CLEVER (3) slashing run third-up when launched late from back in the field with a narrow second over 1600m at Wyong. Finds an easier contest and a win looks imminent. APADANA (7) snagged back from the wide draw and failed to get into the contest when ninth over 1400m at Hawkesbury. Gets a better set-up in this suitable contest. JOIKA (9) drawn out at both career starts and she gets a more economical run today. Went back from the wide gate when a battling tenth over 1600m at Scone. Expected to play a leading role here.
